video.title: Molang
video.synopsis: An imaginative, big-hearted bunny and his friend, a playful chick, explore the everyday joys of their pastel-colored world.

episodes.synopsis: While getting dressed up for a party, Piu Piu gets self-conscious about his unruly feathers -- until Molang switches up his look.
episodes.title: The Party

episodes.synopsis: When Piu Piu struggles to keep up with his friends on a bike ride, Molang cycles through a few solutions.
episodes.title: The Bicycle Ride

episodes.synopsis: Stranded at sea and looking for land, Molang tries to keep a lifeboat -- and Piu Piu's hopes -- afloat.
episodes.title: The Castaways

episodes.synopsis: Eager to ride with their friends in the desert, Molang and Piu Piu have trouble mounting a camel.
episodes.title: The Camel

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu disturb the peace on the beach when they try to crack open a coconut.
episodes.title: The Coconut

episodes.synopsis: The friends are ready for fun in the sun! But before they can go on vacation, Molang must figure out what to pack and what to leave.
episodes.title: The Suitcase

episodes.synopsis: When Molang accidentally throws their little Christmas tree into the fire to keep warm, he and his friends search for another one to decorate.
episodes.title: The Christmas Tree

episodes.synopsis: With their pet goldfish bored in its bowl, Molang and Piu Piu try to find it a friend.
episodes.title: The Goldfish

episodes.synopsis: Surf's up for Molang and Piu Piu when they hit the beach to ride the waves -- until Molang loses his cap.
episodes.title: The Beach

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu's peaceful fishing trip goes sideways when the duo is chased by flies and Molang gets stuck in quicksand.
episodes.title: The Fishing Trip

episodes.synopsis: When Molang and Piu Piu search for the perfect place to pitch their tent, issues arise in every spot.
episodes.title: The Campers

episodes.synopsis: After inviting their friends over to watch a soccer game on their new TV, Molang and Piu Piu experience technical difficulties while setting it up.
episodes.title: The Television

episodes.synopsis: Molang's nighttime routine keeps Piu Piu from getting shut-eye, so Molang tries soothing him to sleep.
episodes.title: The Sleepless Night

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu put their household trinkets up for sale at a street fair.
episodes.title: The Second-hand Market

episodes.synopsis: When a special delivery arrives, Molang and Piu Piu must trudge through the snow to retrieve it.
episodes.title: The Parcel

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu's picnic in the park turns into a pursuit for a fluttery creature.
episodes.title: The Butterfly

episodes.synopsis: Piu Piu prepares a package for Molang -- but Molang must wait till his friends arrive to open it. And waiting turns out to be a tough task.
episodes.title: The Surprise

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu explore the forest to collect mushrooms but wind up getting lost in an unfamiliar place.
episodes.title: The Forest

episodes.synopsis: When Piu Piu carves a pumpkin for Halloween, he hands it to a friend disguised as a mummy -- only to realize it's not Molang.
episodes.title: The Pumpkin

episodes.synopsis: After their armchair breaks, Molang and Piu Piu hunt for a comfy seat at the secondhand market. Their next challenge: bringing it home.
episodes.title: The Armchair

episodes.synopsis: After hearing Piu Piu sing, Molang sets up a recital for him to perform. But once Piu Piu hits the stage, no sound comes out of his beak.
episodes.title: Stage Fright

episodes.synopsis: At a ranch, Molang and Piu Piu work together to wrangle cattle and a wild horse that has them running all over the field.
episodes.title: The Cowboys

episodes.synopsis: A joyride on motorcycles turns into a road trip to the Grand Canyon when Molang, Piu Piu and their friends race to recover Piu Piu's bandana.
episodes.title: The Bandanna

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu's Antarctic adventure leads to a very close encounter with a group of waddling, fish-loving animals.
episodes.title: The Penguin

episodes.synopsis: Owners of a shiny, yellow convertible, Molang and Piu Piu drive to a picnic with their friends only to lose their food supply -- and their new car.
episodes.title: The Car

episodes.synopsis: A strange sound coming out of Piu Piu's beak keeps him from dancing with his friends onstage.
episodes.title: The Hiccup

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu scour a mountain for a rare flower. But the uphill climb leaves Molang exhausted, forcing Piu Piu to tackle the mission solo.
episodes.title: The Mountain Bloom

episodes.synopsis: After Molang and Piu Piu host a monster movie night with their friends, strange noises in the living room keep them awake.
episodes.title: A Restless Night

episodes.synopsis: At an excavation site, Molang and Piu Piu realize that digging for fossils is hard work -- until they make a massive discovery.
episodes.title: The Archaeologists

episodes.synopsis: During a game of ice hockey, Molang, Piu Piu and their friends are put in danger when the ice on the frozen lake begins to crack.
episodes.title: The Hockey Game

episodes.synopsis: A storm rains on Molang and Piu Piu's camping trip, forcing them and their friends to find shelter in a spooky abandoned castle.
episodes.title: The Castle

episodes.synopsis: At a sheep pen, Molang and Piu Piu try to assist a shepherd but their help just causes disaster.
episodes.title: The Shepherds

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu cross paths with a lost pup, who won't stop following them.
episodes.title: The Puppy

episodes.synopsis: When Molang and Piu Piu visit an underground cave, their picture taking disrupts the tour. Then, they find themselves lost among the many tunnels.
episodes.title: The Underground Walk

episodes.synopsis: When Molang and Piu Piu oversee their friend's hotel for one night, they stop at nothing to meet a guest's endless needs.
episodes.title: The Hotel

episodes.synopsis: After finding a treasure map at the secondhand market, Molang and Piu Piu embark on an adventure in the jungle, where many surprises await.
episodes.title: The Explorers

episodes.synopsis: Determined to take a photo of his favorite football player, Piu Piu and Molang head to the stadium to find him but have a hard time keeping up.
episodes.title: The Football Player

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu order a robot to help take care of chores. But when the robot starts imitating their friends at a party, it starts to go haywire.
episodes.title: The Robot

episodes.synopsis: During an intense game of rugby, Molang and Piu Piu compete on opposing teams but find it difficult to stop helping each other.
episodes.title: A Friendly Rugby Game

episodes.synopsis: When Molang and Piu Piu dress up as firemen for a dance party, they get caught up in a real emergency involving a giraffe that escapes from the circus.
episodes.title: The Firemen

episodes.synopsis: At the beach, Molang and Piu Piu's friends suggest playing badminton. But when they walk to the van to get their rackets, they find something's missing.
episodes.title: The Keys

episodes.synopsis: To escape the rumbling of construction work on their street, Molang and Piu Piu look for peace and quiet elsewhere.
episodes.title: The Lighthouse

episodes.synopsis: When a feathered friend lands on Molang and Piu Piu's rooftop, the two pals help their new neighbor build a nest.
episodes.title: The Stork

episodes.synopsis: When Molang accidentally breaks Piu Piu's colorful statue, he and his friends try to distract Piu Piu as they piece it back together.
episodes.title: The Statue

episodes.synopsis: In Mollywood, Molang and Piu Piu act as extras on set -- but disaster strikes when the cameras start rolling.
episodes.title: The Movie

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu take on lifeguard duty at the beach and handle every crisis that comes their way.
episodes.title: The Rescuers

episodes.synopsis: While on their way to the beach, Molang and Piu Piu get caught in heavy traffic and decide to have a roadside picnic instead.
episodes.title: Traffic Jam

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu find a lonely baby seal and try to protect it when something big under the ice starts to approach them.
episodes.title: The Baby Seal

episodes.synopsis: An old friend comes to stay with Molang and Piu Piu but messes seem to follow him everywhere. Later, his clumsiness turns out to be a talent.
episodes.title: The Guest

episodes.synopsis: Molang and Piu Piu attempt to catch a giant fish until something bigger lands in their net.
episodes.title: An Extraordinary Catch

episodes.synopsis: While on a winter vacation with their friends, Molang and Piu Piu try to find their balance on a ski lift.
episodes.title: Skiing

episodes.synopsis: After being scouted by a talent agent, Molang and Piu Piu hit the big time with their dance moves -- until they start missing their quiet life at home.
episodes.title: Superstars
